{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Auschwitz was, to me, a horrendous place, because I saw my dad getting beat, beaten up, to the point where he just could not-- in fact, we were standing in an appel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was trying to, somehow, come over to my side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And for some unknown reason, they got on him, and they just started beating him unmercifully.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I tried--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the-- at that point, it was Germans and kapos both.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to run out, and they give-- they hit me a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my uncles, you know, grabbed me and, and, and just held me back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was just doing it from the reaction of a child seeing his father getting beaten up to the point where he was just bleeding from every which way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they were pouring cold water on him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that causes a heart-- I didn't know that-- I mean, but that was another method for them to kill you, is that they beat you to a point where your system gets so overheated, or your blood, or whatever it is, and then you pull water on somebody.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I guess it causes some shock or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned that later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so then, I had to cope with that, because we brought him back to the barracks, and he was just in agony.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He just could not-- and he just kept-- he just could not move in or out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had to drag himself out for the appels, and his ribs were broken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was just-- he was just dying, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And along with everything else that was happening, my father was suffering, you know, under, under these conditions.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
